#alias: #MATLAB group_name from utest_csvs.csv (any one of the aliases for a csv group).
varName: MATLAB variable name. Accepts nested tables as var.subname.
varNcol: Number of delimiter-separated columns in variable with delimiters specified in the CSV list.
formatSpec: MATLAB formatspec. do not use * to skip
isSaved: Save the column for MATLAB (or delete it). Use this rather than formatspec * to skip columns to ensure writeability.
